title: WordPress Fitness Theme eCommerce
description:
Fitness is a Gym and sport WordPress Theme designed in a minimalist style. It has a responsive layout that looks great on mobile and tablet devices. Fitness Wordpress Theme is Wordpress and eCommerce for Fitness, Gym and Sport Clubs.

Fitness WordPress Theme and eCommerce is built for Gym, Fitness Clubs, Personal Trainers, Health Centers and other sport and health related business and it is suitable for any kind of sport activity like Marathon event, Dance school, Boxing classes, Crossfit and Martial arts.
